videos.description: Illinois guard Trent Frazier gets the steal, waits for a teammate to join him, then throws the behind-the-back pass to Andre Curbelo for the layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Illinois' Frazier goes behind-the-back to Curbelo for the layup) 2020/12/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Illinois' Frazier goes behind-the-back to Curbelo for the layup

videos.description: Missouri gets out in transition off the missed shot and it leads to Javon Pickett flying toward the rim for the dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Missouri's Pickett soars to the rim for the jam) 2020/12/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Missouri's Pickett soars to the rim for the jam

videos.description: Illinois guard Ayo Dosunmu uses his strength to fight through the contact and finish the bucket plus the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Dosunmu fights through the contact for and-1) 2020/12/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dosunmu fights through the contact for and-1

videos.description: Missouri big man Mitchell Smith hustles down the offensive rebound in the corner, then cuts towards the basket for the two-handed jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Smith does it all with offensive rebound and dunk for Missouri) 2020/12/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Smith does it all with offensive rebound and dunk for Missouri

videos.description: Illinois center Kofi Cockburn throws down back-to-back monster dunks cutting Missouri's lead to one.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Back-to-back Cockburn dunks forces Missouri timeout) 2020/12/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Back-to-back Cockburn dunks forces Missouri timeout

videos.description: Ayo Disunmu misses the difficult 3-pointer with under five seconds remaining giving Missouri the upset over No. 6 Illinois.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Dosunmu misses late 3, Mizzou upsets Illinois) 2020/12/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dosunmu misses late 3, Mizzou upsets Illinois
